  - Lad
  - Lad
  dialogue:
  - We were arrogant to think we can tread upon the ocean, take her fruits...
  - ...'n' not expect our deeds to bear consequences.
  - ...
  - Little fish like us aren't meant to swim the same depths as whales, eat the same
    krill, kill the same kraken.
  - I'm heading inside.
  - Don't stay out here too long.
